class="line">  &lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">check</span>(<span class="params"></span>) </span>&#123; </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">var</span> userAgentInfo=navigator.userAgent; </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">var</span> Agents =<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Array</span>(<span class="string">"Android"</span>,<span class="string">"iPhone"</span>,<span class="string">"SymbianOS"</span>,<span class="string">"Windows Phone"</span>,<span class="string">"iPad"</span>,<span class="string">"iPod"</span>); </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">var</span> flag=<span class="literal">true</span>; </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">var</span> v=<span class="number">0</span>;v&lt;Agents.length;v++) &#123; </span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">if</span>(userAgentInfo.indexOf(Agents[v])&gt;<span class="number">0</span>) &#123; </span><br><span class="line">   flag=<span class="literal">false</span>; </span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">break</span>; </span><br><span class="line"> &#125; </span><br><span class="line">   &#125; </span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">return</span> flag; </span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">if</span>(check())&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"PC"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">document</span>.getElementById(<span class="string">"需要隐藏的divID"</span>).style.display=<span class="string">""</span>;<span class="comment">//显示</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;<span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">"NOPC"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">document</span>.getElementById(<span class="string">"需要隐藏的divID"</span>).style.display=<span class="string">"none"</span>;<span class="comment">//隐藏</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;<span class="regexp">/script&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">   ```  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">   - 应用位置  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">   fork me on github添加的路径themes/</span>next/layout/_layout.swig,找到相关div下面粘贴上面代码,修改ID即可.  </span><br><span class="line">   addthis由next集成,路径themes/next/layout/_partials/footer.swig中找到  </span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">``</span><span class="string">`html</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">   &lt;div id="addthis" class="addthis_inline_share_toolbox"&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">   &lt;/div&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>在下面粘贴主要代码,修改为需要隐藏的div的ID即可.<blockquote><p>hexo g -d<br>hexo s</p></blockquote></li></ul></li><li>演示<br><img alt data-src="images/01.jpg"><br><img alt data-src="images/02.jpg"></li></ol><a id="more"></a><p><strong>以此类推,一切都可以这样做.</strong>  </p>]]></content>
    
